---
---

<section class="relative pt-32 pb-16 sm:pt-40 sm:pb-24 md:pt-48 md:pb-36 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-indigo-600/15 rounded-full blur-[140px] pointer-events-none -z-10 animate-pulse-glow"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-1/3 left-1/4 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-purple-600/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none -z-10"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#ffffff05_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#ffffff05_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:4rem_4rem] [mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse_60%_50%_at_50%_0%,#000_70%,transparent_100%)] pointer-events-none -z-10"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-2xl sm:rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider sm:tracking-widest text-indigo-400 mb-6 sm:mb-8 backdrop-blur-md hover:border-indigo-500/40 transition-colors max-w-full text-center leading-tight">
      <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-indigo-500 animate-ping shrink-0"></span>
      <span>Strony WWW + Klienci z Google • Wersja Startowa w 48h</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl font-black uppercase italic tracking-tighter text-white leading-[0.95] sm:leading-[0.88] mb-6 sm:mb-8">
      Strona, która sprzedaje. <br />
      <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-400 via-indigo-200 to-purple-400">
        Od pierwszego dnia.
      </span>
    </h1>

    <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg sm:text-xl text-white/60 font-medium leading-relaxed mb-12">
      Tworzymy szybkie witryny firmowe i od razu uruchamiamy machinę pozyskiwania klientów (SEO + Google Ads). <strong class="text-white">Bez wielkich kosztów na start, w stałym abonamencie i bez długoterminowych umów.</strong>
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3.5 sm:gap-4 mb-12 sm:mb-16">
      <a href="#kalkulator" class="w-full sm:w-auto">
        <button class="w-full sm:w-auto h-13 sm:h-16 px-6 sm:px-10 rounded-full bg-white text-black font-black text-xs sm:text-sm uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-zinc-200 transition-all duration-300 shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(255,255,255,0.25)] hover:shadow-[0_0_70px_rgba(255,255,255,0.4)] active:scale-95 flex items-center justify-center gap-2.5">
          <span>Oblicz wycenę w 60s</span>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
          </svg>
        </button>
      </a>
      <a href="#cennik" class="w-full sm:w-auto">
        <button class="w-full sm:w-auto h-13 sm:h-16 px-6 sm:px-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-white border border-white/10 font-black text-xs sm:text-sm uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white/20 transition-all duration-300 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          <span>Sprawdź abonament od 0 zł</span>
        </button>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
      <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5">
        <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white italic tracking-tighter">0<span class="text-indigo-400"> PLN</span></div>
        <div class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/40 mt-1">Kosztu na start w abonamencie</div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5">
        <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white italic tracking-tighter">48<span class="text-indigo-400">h</span></div>
        <div class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/40 mt-1">Gotowa strona z treściami</div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5">
        <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white italic tracking-tighter">100<span class="text-indigo-400">%</span></div>
        <div class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/40 mt-1">Pełny pakiet działań od 1. dnia</div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5">
        <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white italic tracking-tighter">30<span class="text-indigo-400"> dni</span></div>
        <div class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/40 mt-1">Okres wypowiedzenia (Bez umów)</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
